sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Tekton as Konflux/Tekton<br/>CI/CD Pipeline
    participant Registry as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as rhods-operator<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant IS as ImageStream<br/>(Cluster Resource)
    participant NCtrl as ODH Notebook<br/>Controller
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard

    Note over Dev,Registry: Flow 1: Image Build and Deployment

    Dev->>GH: Push code / PR<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>GitHub token auth
    GH->>Tekton: Webhook trigger<br/>HTTPS/443
    Tekton->>GH: Clone source<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>GitHub token
    Tekton->>Tekton: Build container images<br/>(94 pipeline variants)
    Tekton->>Registry: Push images<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Registry credentials
    Operator->>K8s: Apply ImageStream manifests<br/>(kustomize render)<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>IS: ImageStreams created

    Note over Dev,Dashboard: Flow 2: User Workbench Session

    participant User as User Browser
    participant GW as OpenShift Gateway<br/>(Envoy) 443/TCP
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant JL as JupyterLab Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP

    User->>GW: Access workbench<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>OIDC/OAuth auth
    GW->>KRBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS<br/>RBAC SubjectAccessReview
    KRBAC->>JL: Proxy to workbench<br/>HTTP/8888, plaintext (localhost)<br/>Trusted (same pod)
    JL-->>KRBAC: Response
    KRBAC-->>GW: Encrypted response
    GW-->>User: Workbench UI

    Note over JL,K8s: Workbench → Cluster Operations
    JL->>K8s: oc CLI / K8s SDK calls<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token

    Note over NCtrl,IS: Controller Image Resolution
    NCtrl->>IS: Read ImageStream tags<br/>HTTPS/6443
    IS-->>NCtrl: Image references
    NCtrl->>Registry: Pull workbench image<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Pull secret
    Dashboard->>IS: Query ImageStream annotations<br/>HTTPS/6443
    IS-->>Dashboard: Available notebook list
